{"tid":1287541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]沙打區選民請入","createTime":"2019-07-05T08:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T16:10:08.000Z","uid":194830,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ee9d71bc4815eb17ab798b2b4fa5b889fedcde32","tid":1287541,"uid":194830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:56:51.000Z","msg":"眾所周知，沙打區有賴村民支持一直由溫和輝做區議員。但佢咁多年乜撚都冇做過，日日剩係同人去飲茶同掛banner。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2017/05/05/127418/i_640x961_041610706.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F127418%2Fi_640x961_041610706.jpg&h=72dc6c71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年，佢終於唔撚選！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民建聯今年推左高維基出黎準備接任。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/10343011_770473593007338_778861581337086939_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_oc=AQnIHp9pJGVZvDjIARPrsKYwE_eeuL2BjOdDrRUidaleCUY7w1-aHj25fxgtjnkk8I0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=7d00a3496be073cbf4725db915e13cf8&amp;oe=5DBD835B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F10343011_770473593007338_778861581337086939_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_oc%3DAQnIHp9pJGVZvDjIARPrsKYwE_eeuL2BjOdDrRUidaleCUY7w1-aHj25fxgtjnkk8I0%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D7d00a3496be073cbf4725db915e13cf8%26oe%3D5DBD835B&h=4713ff78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高維基係邊個？我都唔撚知。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wepost.hk/posts/770473756340655/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwepost.hk%2Fposts%2F770473756340655%2F&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=16c0cb99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wepost.hk/posts/770473756340655/</a><br />\n<br />\n「在香港，大學生一般最希望畢業後在中環上班，能進入投資銀行工作更羨煞同儕，即時與「金融才俊」劃上等號。高維基便是此類人，但令人出乎意料的是，<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">二十九歲的他竟毅然辭去投資銀行職位</span></span></strong></strong>，由中環返回成長之地沙頭角，重新摸索自己的人生目標，嘗試創業，學習從政，決心找尋屬於自己不一樣的人生意義。<br />\n離開中環尋找自我<br />\n很少年青人這麼熱愛自己居住的社區，高維基對沙頭角的感情，甚至讓他辭去令人艶羨的工作，回到「山旮旯」的沙頭角創業從政，到底是甚麼驅使他作出這樣的一個決定？高維基直言，一切為了找回「自我」。<br />\n他說︰「我以前在中環返銀行，做了三至四年投資銀行證劵，以前總是覺得做投資銀行能賺到錢，時間久了，卻發覺自己活得沒有目標。到底晚晚通宵工作，做得這樣辛苦是為了甚麼呢？我要追求的是甚麼？」<br />\n那段時期，他周末一有時間便會幫沙頭角現任區議員溫和達做社區服務，一時賣旗，一時做義工，久而久之對服務社區產生了濃厚的興趣。他回憶與溫生的相識︰「我家租住沙頭角近十年，父親與溫生熟悉，<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我由細便經常幫溫生做義工，我視他為半個父親，也是師傅。</span></span></strong></strong>」」<br />\n<br />\n如果今年俾佢選到，好有可能佢就會做另一個溫和輝佔據沙打多廿年。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地唔可以俾佢發生。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2015年沙打區選舉冇一個係民主派，但温和輝仍然大比數勝出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>1 温和輝 2,307*</strong><br />\n2 曾玉安 1,104<br />\n3 張貴財 651<br />\n4 朱愛平 111<br />\n<br />\n作為民建聯票倉嘅沙打，2016立法會選舉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「位於新界邊陲的沙打（N16）選區包括羅湖、文錦渡、打鼓嶺及沙頭角等鄉郊地區。未計算獨立參選的方國珊，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建制派候選人總得票為2,453，以1,340票拋離泛民和自決派候選人</span></span>。不過這區的「票王」不是鄉事派的侯志強，而是奪1,407票的民建聯陳克勤。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/立法會選舉/42306/立會選戰-數據-非建制得票輸建制-解構1成-深紅-選區\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%2F42306%2F%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E6%88%B0-%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A-%E9%9D%9E%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E5%BE%97%E7%A5%A8%E8%BC%B8%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6-%E8%A7%A3%E6%A7%8B1%E6%88%90-%E6%B7%B1%E7%B4%85-%E9%81%B8%E5%8D%80&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=48cbbaed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/立法會選舉/42306/立會選戰-數據-非建制得票輸建制-解構1成-深紅-選區</a><br />\n<br />\n今年我地一定要反抗呢個宿命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先我地要搵個人出黎選。跪求巴打絲打企出黎面對高維基，一眾沙打連登仔會企出黎做街站推倒民建聯。<br />\n<br />\n我地要做嘅野：<br />\n1\b. 搵人出選<br />\n2. 組織街站<br />\n3. 說服原居民放棄民建聯<br />\n<br />\n希望11月會見到個黃色嘅沙頭角<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7f7af5a857ff35cffbf328516296764bedbfef","tid":1287541,"uid":194830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:57:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb23c0da5300a0b6d21e2729258d42efd7ac1d91","tid":1287541,"uid":194830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:57:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bee090a7262113819fbbc4e6ddc734d395a7e374","tid":1287541,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:58:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc6169efafc3aa56a84d2f781d0fed0d7becdeb","tid":1287541,"uid":194830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:59:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4882b0e291e26604760b13b21f34169c7d9f3667","tid":1287541,"uid":194830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:59:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fa2e5a1cde262ebf4766e3b1be3de7e46a2ac82","tid":1287541,"uid":233929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:00:15.000Z","msg":"支持打破一切攏壟斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2b599eef92f2fc143b99dd9a6d5621279d5e48","tid":1287541,"uid":194830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:02:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0889f0e264210aea997acfdee4755811bb775144","tid":1287541,"uid":171578,"like":0,"