dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:44:13.000Z","msg":"你地區內多唔多35以下？"},{"pid":"703d578731ab72d65748a011d11db80a02c179ff","tid":1287541,"uid":264369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:46:52.000Z","msg":"支持坐言起行<br />\n即時開始踢走保皇工程"},{"pid":"dc7ce7c914f3e72fc4160f713f0ed7950c85d6e0","tid":1287541,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e010861971bf17367ef0290a84c36bf727f8c4","tid":1287541,"uid":197011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:38:42.000Z","msg":"沙打區巴絲打<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/timtim2446\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftimtim2446&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=defa215d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/timtim2446</a><br />\n希望大家可以幫手"},{"pid":"1c659c8b0fe5a6e731567aba7e1c8e1accef7b7c","tid":1287541,"uid":334925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:30:15.000Z","msg":"時代革命！光復沙頭角！"},{"pid":"90b837be4df72250595418193a035ca84ac2ed5f","tid":1287541,"uid":323685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T12:40:13.000Z","msg":"有無人想搞個沙打區tg group 😂"},{"pid":"5ca8cc07f460b0f2f9010e26dbe35046cae1bcaa","tid":1287541,"uid":209146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33e9cf2ef9d46d42cfdede2a1155bacacfd70d53","tid":1287541,"uid":194830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c26a204a8aba6b34622792102342c12ef6b61c92","tid":1287541,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:05:44.000Z","msg":"你地選完，組唔組織到人手去服務果區居民先？<br />\n講緊沙頭角wor大佬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:09:08.000Z","msg":"所以最好係搵到沙頭角巴絲一齊做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:38:08.000Z","msg":"TG?"},{"pid":"bcde69bc298bc52b54f955814217